we are seeing the power of economic freedom spreading around the 
world places such as the republic of korea singapore taiwan have 
vaulted into the technological era barely pausing in the 
industrial age along the way lowtax agricultural policies in the 
subcontinent mean that in some years india is now a net exporter 
