goes forward 
the empress ii is equipped with two diesel generators and a huge 
antenna system capable of sending pulses of electrical power 
into the atmosphere at power levels up to 7 million volts to test a 
phenomenon known as electromagnetic pulse or emp 
the navy maintains the testing will have no affect on human or 
marine life 
