paragraph that he proposed and it has been achieved and improved 
to the point that it is clear and unmistakable that it achieves 
the purpose that he had in mind 
q whats the substitute the better term your aides have 
advised you to use 
a no peaceful coexistence both pieces achieved the same end 
but the other one had ambiguities in it and i dont think it was 
