<TEXT>
by muting his criticism of soviet human rights 
abuses president reagan may be trying to speed up negotiations 
that would substantially cut red army forces in eastern europe 
reagan who built a political career bashing reds and in his 
first term called the soviet union an evil empire confounded 
observers on tuesday and wednesday by attributing kremlin human 
