derailed and tumbled down an embankment after hitting the 
gravelladen train in southwestern netherlands at about 1040 am 
said spokesman hans meijer 
he said the 39yearold locomotive engineer of the passenger 
train was killed as was a 79yearold dutch woman identified as 
a sitter 
