tuesday by the departments agricultural statistics board a year 
ago the index was 128 
higher prices for hogs oranges soybeans and broilers were 
partially offset by lower prices for tomatoes onions milk and 
upland cotton it said 
hog prices reached their highest levels since october while 
cattle rose to their highest since may 1979 soybeans shot up 
sharply 
